column16: Caleb Joseph homers (5) on a fly ball to left center field.

Michael Taylor homers (5) on a fly ball to right field.    Ian Desmond scores.
Ian Desmond grounds into a force out, third baseman Chase Headley to second baseman Stephen Drew.   Yunel Escobar out at 2nd.    Ian Desmond to 1st.
Bryce Harper flies out to left fielder Chris Young.
Kirk Nieuwenhuis called out on strikes.
David Freese grounds out, second baseman Stephen Drew to first baseman Mark Teixeira.
Welington Castillo grounds out, third baseman Chase Headley to first baseman Mark Teixeira.
Logan Morrison reaches on a missed catch error by pitcher Jacob Lindgren, assist to first baseman Mark Teixeira.
Stephen Vogt out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Brett Gardner.   Billy Burns scores.  Sam Fuld advances to 2nd, on a throwing error by center fielder Brett Gardner.
Andy Parrino strikes out swinging, catcher Brian McCann to first baseman Garrett Jones.
Billy Burns singles on a ground ball to second baseman Stephen Drew.   Josh Phegley to 3rd.
Mark Canha pops out to third baseman Chase Headley.
Josh Phegley doubles (2) on a fly ball to center fielder Chris Young.
Josh Reddick grounds out, pitcher Jacob Lindgren to first baseman Garrett Jones.

Alcides Escobar flies out to right fielder Garrett Jones.
Salvador Perez lines out to center fielder Slade Heathcott.
Eric Hosmer grounds into a double play, second baseman Jose Pirela to shortstop Didi Gregorius to first baseman Garrett Jones.   Jarrod Dyson out at 2nd.
